OL,3,CKey rival of Turkish President Erdogan
OL,4,Carrested amid opposition crackdown
OL,6,FIstanbul's mayor, a popular opposition
OL,7,Fleader and key rival of President
OL,8,FRecep Tayyip Erdogan, was arrested on
OL,9,FWednesday.
OL,11,FSeveral other prominent figures were
OL,12,Falso arrested, as part of
OL,13,Finvestigations into alleged corruption
OL,14,Fand terror links.
OL,16,FThe arrests are a dramatic escalation
OL,17,Fof a government crackdown on the
OL,18,Fopposition and dissenting voices in
OL,19,FTurkey.
