OL,3,CKey rival of Turkish President Erdogan
OL,4,Carrested amid opposition crackdown
OL,6,FThe state-run Anadolu Agency said
OL,7,Fprosecutors issued detention warrants
OL,8,Ffor the mayor, Ekrem Imamoglu, and
OL,9,Fsome 100 other people.
OL,11,FAmong those detained was Imamoglu's
OL,12,Fclose aide, Murat Ongun.
OL,14,FAuthorities also closed several roads
OL,15,Faround Istanbul and banned
OL,16,Fdemonstrations in the city for four
OL,17,Fdays in an apparent effort to prevent
OL,18,Fprotests following the arrest.
