OL,3,CKey rival of Turkish President Erdogan
OL,4,Carrested amid opposition crackdown
OL,6,FCritics say the crackdown follows
OL,7,Fsignificant losses by Erdogan's ruling
OL,8,Fparty in local elections last year,
OL,9,Famid growing calls for early national
OL,10,Felections.
OL,12,FGovernment officials insist that the
OL,13,Fcourts operate independently and
OL,14,Freject claims that legal actions
OL,15,Fagainst opposition figures are
OL,16,Fpolitically motivated.
